<div class="WordSection1"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Pte.Ltd.</span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">2 Loyang Crescent</span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">508976 Singapore </span></div>
<div class="WordSection1">
<p><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">June 29, 2015<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>
<p><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Dear Honeywell Customer, </span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: black;">Honeywell Aerospace is constantly looking to improve its business processes and operations in support of its service to our customers, and a key element of this is our strategy to create an integrated business platform via the Honeywell International S&agrave;rl (HIS) organization. </span>This change will simplify the way in which you conduct business with Honeywell and deliver a more efficient and effective procurement experience.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: black;">As an extension of the existing business environment and structure, the business activity currently linked with the </span>Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Pte. Ltd facility (Avionics R&amp;O Site at Loyang site)<span style="color: black;">, will transition to HIS currently targeted for October&nbsp; 2015.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: black;">The Singapore Loyang site</span> is an advanced avionics repair and overhaul shop, supporting a number of products including: Flight Management Systems, Ground Proximity Warning, AIMS, Autopilot, Data Management, Recorders, TCAS, Radar, Indicators, Displays and AOA/LGG Fan/Waste Management.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">The actions associated with this transition will result in a change to the Honeywell legal entity. Although the Singapore Loyang R&amp;O business will operate at the same site, you will need to update the supplier information in your procurement and accounting systems. <br /></span></p>
<p><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: black; font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">We appreciate your understanding and cooperation for a seamless transition for you and your organization. Here are the steps you will need to take:</span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Update your Authorized Supplier List (ASL) and internal systems to reflect the new Honeywell International S&agrave;rl (HIS) legal entity. <br /><br /> </span> 
<ul>
<li><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">The new supplier address for the Singapore Loyang procurement and accounting transactions is:<br /><br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; Honeywell International S&agrave;rl<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; Aerospace R&amp;O<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; Z.A. La Pi&egrave;ce 16,<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; 1180 Rolle, Switzerland<br /> <br /> </span></li>
<li><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">The amended &ldquo;Ship To&rdquo; address for the Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Avionics R&amp;O site is:<br /> <br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; Honeywell International S&agrave;rl<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; C/O Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Pte. Ltd.,<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; 2 Loyang Crescent<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; 508976 Singapore<br /></span></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="WordSection1">
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: windowtext;">For Contract Customers only: Execute an Amendment Agreement to assign Contracts, to include HIS and/or delete HASPL/ HAPL from Contract, to amend Bank details, delivery /export clauses, notices address etc., where required. Our Contracts team has been in contact with your company to provide additional information to complete this action.</span><span style="color: black;"> <br /></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="color: windowtext; font-size: 14px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">As we go through this transition, we want to assure you that we have your best interests in mind and we will provide additional details 60, 30 and 5 days prior October 2015. We have attached a <a href="https://pages3.honeywell.com/rs/641-QIX-912/images/Singapore FAQs 06.27.2015.pdf">frequently asked questions</a> document for this transition.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: windowtext;">For you</span><span style="color: #1f497d;">r</span><span style="color: windowtext;"> information, concurrently as a separate project, we are enhancing the SAP software at other R&amp;O sites in August and October 2015. The August transition will include sites in Tempe, Arizona; Wichita, Kansas; Basingstoke, UK, and Shanghai, China. The October transition will include sites in Renton, Washington; Rocky Mount, North Carolina; Toulouse, France, and Tucson, Arizona. We are providing updates to our customers who conduct business at these sites.</span><span style="color: black;"> </span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: black;">If you have any questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to contact your Honeywell Customer Business Manager or email us at </span><a href="mailto:AeroCPSCommunications@Honeywell.com">AeroCPSCommunications@Honeywell.com</a><span style="color: black;">.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: black; font-size: 14px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Yours sincerely,</span><strong> <br /></strong></p>
</div>
